 We will have Exam 2 in the second week of April (11th, 13th, or 15th).  It will cover Chapters 3, 4 (including PV diagrams), and 5.  If there is a day of that week that you <b>don't</b> want the exam to be (due to other exams, projects, etc), please email me before April 6th which is when I will announce the date of the exam.
<li>
